<c74object name='sp.lpg~' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Vactrol/low pass gate model
</digest>
    <description>Vactrol/low pass gate model.
</description>
    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.lpg~</o> object is an implementation of a low pass gate, which rolls back the harmonics as well as cutting the volume based on a vactrol model.
</discussion>

